OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,FSince then, the Clean Air Zone signs
OL,6,Fhave been covered with stickers saying
OL,7,F"under review".
OL,9,FIn January 2025, the Government
OL,10,Fapproved plans from local leaders to
OL,11,Fmeet government clean air targets,
OL,12,Farguing that rising costs would stop
OL,13,Fdrivers upgrading their vehicles.
OL,15,FTransport for Greater Manchester
OL,16,F(TfGM) has now confirmed that work has
OL,17,Fbegun to take the signs down.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
