OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,FIn a report, transport bosses said
OL,6,Fthat 'the release of funds' for
OL,7,Fcouncils to remove or repurpose the
OL,8,Fsigns, has been approved.
OL,10,FClean air campaigners criticised the
OL,11,Fdecision to scrap the scheme, claiming
OL,12,Fthat it is contributing to an
OL,13,F'epidemic' of serious lung problems
OL,14,Fand respiratory illnesses, but Greater
OL,15,FManchester mayor Andy Burnham insists
OL,16,Fcharging motorists would not have
OL,17,Fhelped.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
