OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,FThe Federation of Small Businesses
OL,6,F(FSB) has welcomed the signs coming
OL,7,Fdown, saying that the scheme is
OL,8,F"finally being put to bed".
OL,10,FRobert Downes, FSB's development
OL,11,Fmanager in Greater Manchester, said:
OL,12,F"While we've known the CAZ was all but
OL,13,Fdead and buried quite some time ago,
OL,14,Fit's symbolic and definitive to learn
OL,15,Fthat plans are now in motion to bring
OL,16,Fdown the signage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
