OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,F"Despite all the effort we put in to
OL,6,Fopposing the CAZ it was, ironically,
OL,7,Fthe signs going up in the first place
OL,8,Fthat triggered the massive reaction
OL,9,Ffrom both the business community and
OL,10,Fthe wider public when they woke up to
OL,11,Fthe huge financial implications of
OL,12,Fwhat was being proposed.
OL,14,F"You only now have to look around the
OL,15,Fcountry to see other city regions who
OL,16,Frushed ahead with similar schemes to
OL,17,Fsee how they have hammered businesses,
OL,18,Fmany of whom have been forced to close
OL,19,Fbecause of the unavoidable costs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
