OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,F"While it may have taken local
OL,6,Fdecision makers a while to come
OL,7,Faround, it's always better late than
OL,8,Fnever."
OL,10,FThe Clean Air Zone would have seen
OL,11,Ftaxis, vans, lorries and buses that
OL,12,Fdon't meet emissions standards charged
OL,13,Fup to #60 a day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
