OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,FUnder the new "investment-led"
OL,6,Fapproach, there will no charges.
OL,7,FInstead, the government has allowed
OL,8,FGreater Manchester to spend #86m on a
OL,9,Fseries of other initiatives including
OL,10,Fgrants to upgrade vehicles and
OL,11,Fmeasures to reduce traffic around the
OL,12,Fcity centre.
OL,14,FThe lion's share of this funding will
OL,15,Fgo towards zero emission and cleaner
OL,16,Fdiesel buses which transport bosses
OL,17,Fsay is already helping.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
