OL,3,CSigns come down for Clean Air Zone
OL,5,FMore than 300 electric buses are now
OL,6,Fin use across Greater Manchester's Bee
OL,7,FNetwork with plans to fully electrify
OL,8,Fthe fleet by 2030.
OL,10,FTfGM says this has contributed to air
OL,11,Fpollution dropping again in 2024.
OL,12,FHowever, 38 places still had illegal
OL,13,Flevels of nitrogen dioxide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
